### World of Books Scraper API Requests
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code

@apiUrl = http://localhost:4001/api
@wobUrl = https://www.worldofbooks.com

### 1. Quick Start - Scrape World of Books Navigation
POST {{apiUrl}}/scraper/scrape-worldofbooks

### 2. Trigger Navigation Scrape
POST {{apiUrl}}/scraper/trigger
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUrl": "{{wobUrl}}",
  "targetType": "navigation"
}

### 3. Trigger Category Scrape (adjust URL to actual category)
POST {{apiUrl}}/scraper/trigger
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUrl": "{{wobUrl}}/categories/fiction",
  "targetType": "category"
}

### 4. Trigger Product Scrape (adjust URL to actual product)
POST {{apiUrl}}/scraper/trigger
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUrl": "{{wobUrl}}/product/sample-book-123",
  "targetType": "product"
}

### 5. Get All Scrape Jobs
GET {{apiUrl}}/scraper/jobs

### 6. Get Specific Job Status (replace with actual jobId)
@jobId = clzt1234567890
GET {{apiUrl}}/scraper/job/{{jobId}}

### 7. Get All Products
GET {{apiUrl}}/products

### 8. Get Products with Pagination
GET {{apiUrl}}/products?skip=0&limit=10

### 9. Get All Navigation
GET {{apiUrl}}/navigation

### 10. Get All Categories
GET {{apiUrl}}/categories

### 11. Get Single Product (replace with actual productId)
@productId = clzt1234567890
GET {{apiUrl}}/products/{{productId}}

### 12. Health Check
GET {{apiUrl}}/health
